item.title: Latest Update April 24, 2024
item.description: I have been on this big big big projects for over a year now, it is like that’s my only life, nothing else, I felt like I was living under a rock for over a year. This project has been a mess from the start. Letting the client run the whole show was a mistake, and it was a mistake that I cannot reverse by the time I got onto the project.
